{"tid":634231,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"被旁人誤會我有臭味 左右做人難","createTime":"2018-04-19T04:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T05:55:14.000Z","uid":99607,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9f493bf56c21ec8cba8c401194da6ab1dcbf6214","tid":634231,"uid":99607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T04:39:07.000Z","msg":"話說有晚做完運動搭地鐵<br />\n咁見到有2個位就坐啦<br />\n當時我第一眼係見到有個MK妹 咁二話不說緊係坐係MK妹隔離 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當我坐落去個下 我知道出事了 <br />\n我朋友一身臭汗味(仲要著住背心 D酸味湧到過嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n但唔坐都坐左 調位又唔好意思 企起身又好怪<br />\n<br />\n當時既座位分佈<br />\n&lt;--- 風向 ---    MK妹 | 我 | 朋友 [玻璃]    --- 地鐵方向 ---&gt;<br />\n<br />\n之後最慘係 我望到我隔離個MK妹同人Whatsapp 話佢隔離個人好臭！！<br />\n我屌！！！！！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地身邊有無有臭味重既朋友<br />\n你地仲會唔會繼續做朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b99e80b836deb157c8ac025972e2982fefc40e","tid":634231,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T04:40:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"597a1e86ba30331e26e7a9ac50111a86b65fea1f","tid":634231,"uid":99607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30b99e80b836deb157c8ac025972e2982fefc40e","tid":634231,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T04:40:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T04:41:57.000Z","msg":"唔是我囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856f0231fea65d4cf5627079292dba9f387bcad8","tid":634231,"uid":57554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T04:44:23.000Z","msg":"做完運動岀完汗臭味點都有<br />\n呢個我相信絕大部份人都係<br />\n問題係，有好多人會帶毛巾抹身同用止汗劑，如